{
  "stem": "24171.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Inside the house, was-- I myself took the cows like a few days before.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a certain place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And all the Jewish people had to bring their-- whoever had cows.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The-- the chickens, and the geese, and the ducks, that was left to whatever.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were roaming around in the-- in the yard or in the backyard or wherever.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But those, they took away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I remember that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I myself went there and helped my father, well, mother.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Well, I was always helping out from my father because that's what-- mother was in the house.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so when they started to open the house and to confiscate whatever was useful for them from the house, the furniture and clothing, whatever, valuables, whatever, well, we tried to hide-- to give some for the other neighborhoods to hide.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But it was very strict, because every-- every day, we didn't have like here at the radio and they announce on the radio the news, wherever it's going on in-- in the city of wherever.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We had a town crier.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "In the good times, too, if something came up, news for the-- you know, that the village has to be repaired, something.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "In the good times, there was a town crier.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That's what they call it, with a--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was in a-- in a-- what is it called?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like the musicians have it, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Gee.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so they were kind of warning the Gentile people that whoever is gonna take something to hide for the Jewish people, they are gonna be punished.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we hid.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they took out from the house everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that was in '30-- in '39 when the Hungarians came in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, because they-- let me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have to think about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
